Rat Sightings Maps

NYC Rat Sightings, 2022

pal <- colorFactor(
  palette = "viridis",
  domain = map_rat_sightings$borough)

map2022<-map_rat_sightings %>% 
  filter(year=="2022") %>% 
  leaflet() %>% 
  addProviderTiles(providers$CartoDB.Positron) %>% 
  addCircleMarkers( lat = ~latitude,  
        lng = ~longitude, radius = .1)

map2022
